<div class="rounded greyish-bg p-4 mb-1">
    <h3 class="text-center">Contribute!</h3>
    <hr />
<p>
  You can contribute to this database in several ways.
  <ul style="line-height: 3;">
    <li>
      <b>Submit new questions</b>. (Please make sure that a similar question does not already exist).
      <br>
      <%= link_to t('submit_a_new_question'), new_question_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg multilinebutton" %>
    </li>
    <li>
      <b>Submit new arguments to questions.</b>
      <br>
        <%= link_to t('show_questions_with_no_or_few_arguments'), overview_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg multilinebutton" %>
      <br>
    </li>
    <li>
      <b>Translate existing questions and answers into new languages.</b>
    </li>
    <li>
      <b>Give feedback.</b> Bad design? Missing features? Missing language? Suggestion for improvements?
      <br>
      <%= link_to t('give_feedback'), contact_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg multilinebutton" %>
    </li>
  </ul>
</p>
</div>
